scala&amp;gt; parquetFile(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;testParquet&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).count()
14/09/15 14:34:17 WARN scheduler.DAGScheduler: Creating &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; stage failed due to exception - job: 0
java.lang.NullPointerException
